WEBVTT

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Rogerson

00:00:09.533 --> 00:00:12.100
So you never believed me from the beginning?

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:17.166
From the beginning you thought I betrayed you because of money

00:00:18.733 --> 00:00:21.166
That's why you humiliated me with money

00:00:26.466 --> 00:00:27.600
Isn't it?

00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:30.800
You are so childish

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:45.300
Lu Zesheng

00:00:46.733 --> 00:00:48.500
I wish you and Yu Qianni

00:00:50.066 --> 00:00:51.600
Happiness forever

00:01:20.966 --> 00:01:22.566
What's wrong dad

00:01:22.666 --> 00:01:24.000
You ask what's wrong?

00:01:24.100 --> 00:01:26.033
The Lus have already arrived at the hotel

00:01:26.133 --> 00:01:28.733
What about you, the Lu family?

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:32.300
Dad?

00:01:33.333 --> 00:01:35.066
I don't want to mess around.

00:01:35.166 --> 00:01:36.466
Even if you don't want to marry

00:01:36.700 --> 00:01:39.400
You must also be there today

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:51.000
Anyway, Lu Zesheng loves meeting you so much

00:01:51.900 --> 00:01:53.800
He will never go

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:56.133
Then what am I afraid of?

00:02:02.566 --> 00:02:04.533
Mom, I don't need a marriage

00:02:07.500 --> 00:02:08.866
This has nothing to do with Yu Qianying

00:02:08.966 --> 00:02:10.300
I don't like him!

00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:26.300
Sorry, the little girl is ignorant.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:27.733
Let you wait for wine

00:02:36.166 --> 00:02:37.000
It's you

00:02:37.100 --> 00:02:39.166
I'm going to marry the daughter of someone like you

00:02:39.566 --> 00:02:42.533
Mr. Lu, please pay attention to your words when you speak

00:02:42.900 --> 00:02:44.166
Talk to you

00:02:44.266 --> 00:02:46.100
I don't think it's necessary to be very particular about words

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:48.933
Sorry for being late.

00:02:53.666 --> 00:02:54.866
Why are you here?

00:02:57.133 --> 00:02:59.800
What is Lin Xinnuo up to?

00:03:00.266 --> 00:03:01.400
Introduce

00:03:01.766 --> 00:03:04.500
This is my daughter Lin Xinnuo